description: Brother Bear is bringing 100% authentic BBQ through New York, New Jersey, Pennsylvania, and Delaware! These trucks are firing up a superb selection of hand-rubbed and mouthwatering meats. Spare ribs, pulled pork sandwiches, sandwiches, sides, sauces, and much more! Whatever you're craving, you're sure to find something to satisfy your wild appetite at Brother Bear's BBQ!
name: Brother Bear's BBQ & Catering
